OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA wet and breezy morning,
OL,6,Fbut brightening up during the
OL,7,Fafternoon with a mixture of sunshine
OL,8,Fand showers. Showers turning heavy,
OL,9,Fwith possible hail and thunder.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FA
OL,12,Fbright start Sunday, but cloud and
OL,13,Frain slowly moving south as the day
OL,14,Fprogresses. Rain clearing to sunny
OL,15,Fspells later Monday. Sunshine and
OL,16,Fshowers following for Tuesday. Average
OL,17,Ftemperatures.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
